high_descs: Walk ahead to the door and then turn right to the white table.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the egg in the right side of the sink.
Turn right and walk ahead and veer right, back to the white table.
Place the egg on the front left corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg on a table.

high_descs: Go straight till end of the kitchen and then turn right towards the white table and two steps to reach the table.
Pick up the white egg at the corner of the white table.
Turn right go straight and then turn right in front of the sink.
Put the egg into the sink and turn on the water until the egg is in the water and then turn off the water and pick up the egg once water is drained.
Turn right go to the end of the kitchen and then turn right towards the white table.
Put the egg on the same place where it was picked from.
anns.task_desc: Take the white egg from the table, wash and return.

high_descs: Cross the room and head to the table on your right.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Turn right and head to the sink.
Put the egg in the sink and turn the faucet on and off, and pick the egg back up.
Turn right and head back to the table.
Place the egg on the table.
anns.task_desc: Wash an egg and put it on the table.
